msgctxt "332"
msgid "Do you want to fish here?"
msgstr "¿Quiere pescar aquí?"

msgctxt "4192"
msgid "Player"
msgstr "Player"

msgctxt "4196"
msgid "Fishing"
msgstr "Pesca"

msgctxt "344_Player"
msgid "(Let's do some fishing.)"
msgstr "(Hora de pescar un poco.)"

msgctxt "368_Player"
msgid "(On second thought... Maybe not.)"
msgstr "(Pensándolo bien... quizá no)."

msgctxt "380_Fishing"
msgid "Select your bait, then decide where to cast your line.\\r\n"\n"\\r\n"\n"Each type of bait has a different range of effect, and the fish won't bite if you use the wrong bait. Items in your possession that can be used as bait will be shown in a list."
msgstr "Seleccione su cebo, después, decida donde lanzar el sedal.\\r\n"\n"\\r\n"\n"Cada tipo de cebo tiene un rango de efecto diferente, y \\r\n"\n"los peces no pican si se usa el cebo incorrecto. Los \\r\n"\n"objetos en su posesión que se puedan usar de cebo se \\r\n"\n"le mostrarán en una lista."

msgctxt "392_Fishing"
msgid "\\r\n"\n"The gauge shows where fish are most concentrated. Use bait that is effective in those areas."
msgstr "\\r\n"\n"The gauge shows where fish are most concentrated. Use bait that is effective in those areas."

msgctxt "404_Fishing"
msgid "Cast your line and wait for a fish to bite.\\r\n"\n"\\r\n"\n"The <Action:Button_Cross@Fishing> icon will appear when a fish is biting. Quickly press <Action:Button_Cross@Fishing> and reel the line in."
msgstr "Lance el sedal y espere a que un pez muerda el anzuelo.\\r\n"\n"\\r\n"\n"El ícono <Action:Button_Cross@Fishing> aparecerá cuando un pez pique. \\r\n"\n"Presione rápidamente <Action:Button_Cross@Fishing> y recoja el sedal."

msgctxt "416_Fishing"
msgid "<Action:Button_R1@Fishing> reels in, while <Action:Button_L1@Fishing> adds slack. Pay attention to the Tension Gauge, and don't let the fish snap your line. Use <Action:Button_LS_Left@Fishing><Action:Button_LS_Right@Fishing>, following the movement of the fish. Move it up and down to raise or lower the pole."
msgstr "<Action:Button_R1@Fishing> enrolla, mientras que <Action:Button_L1@Fishing> suelta. Preste atención al indicador de tensión y no deje que los peces rompan el sedal. Mueva<Action:Button_LS_Left@Fishing><Action:Button_LS_Right@Fishing> siguiendo el movimiento del pez. Mueva arriba y abajo \\r\n"\n"para subir o bajar la caña."

msgctxt "428_Fishing"
msgid "If you control the line's tension and completely reel it in, you will successfully catch the fish."
msgstr "Si controla la tensión del sedal y lo trae entero, \\r\n"\n"capturará el pescado con éxito."

msgctxt "440_Player"
msgid "(I bet there are lots of fish over there...)"
msgstr "(Apuesto a que hay muchos peces por allí...)"

msgctxt "464_Player"
msgid "(All right, let's get the bait ready. This is what I've got with me...)"
msgstr "(Muy bien, a preparar el cebo. Esto es lo que llevo encima...)"

msgctxt "476_Player"
msgid "(I should review the instructions.)"
msgstr "(Debería repasar las instrucciones.)"

msgctxt "488_Player"
msgid "(Maybe later.)"
msgstr "(Tal vez más tarde)."

msgctxt "500_Player"
msgid "(I didn't get a bite...)"
msgstr "(Nada mordió el anzuelo...)"

msgctxt "512_Player"
msgid "(My timing was off...)"
msgstr "(Se me fue la mano...)"

msgctxt "524_Player"
msgid "(The line broke...)"
msgstr "(Se rompió el sedal...)"

msgctxt "536_Player"
msgid "(The fish got away...)"
msgstr "(El pez se escapó...)"

msgctxt "560_Player"
msgid "(I need to put new bait on.)"
msgstr "(Necesito poner cebo nuevo.)"

msgctxt "572_Player"
msgid "(That's enough for now.)"
msgstr "(Es suficiente por ahora.)"

msgctxt "584_Player"
msgid "Go Fishing"
msgstr "Ir de Pesca"

msgctxt "596_Player"
msgid "Don't Fish"
msgstr "No Pescar"

msgctxt "608_Player"
msgid "Go Fishing"
msgstr "Ir de Pesca"

msgctxt "620_Player"
msgid "Read Instructions"
msgstr "Leer las Instrucciones"

msgctxt "632_Player"
msgid "Don't Fish"
msgstr "No Pescar"

msgctxt "644_Player"
msgid "Keep Fishing"
msgstr "Seguir Pescando"

msgctxt "656_Player"
msgid "Stop Fishing"
msgstr "Dejar de Pescar"

